                <head>The Fremont Imbroglio</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Accuses Republican papers of hypocrisy when they accuse Democrats of
                    treason for criticizing Fremont. The Spirit points out that Republicans had
                    denounced him as well.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
